To love China

Reason one

Chinese People - By far the biggest reason I love China. I've made great friends here. True friends. People that I believe that I can count on.

Learn More

Reason two

Chinese Food - HA! Well, it's true. Chinese food is great. I love spicy food. Most people in the world do not realize how spicy the food is in China.

Learn More

Reason three

Chinese Society - I wake up in the morning hearing men yell at the top of their lungs as they exercise in the park next to the river beside my building.

Learn More

Reason four

My Work - I love teaching. I love the challenge of it. I love the challenge of teaching English. It's not easy, but, it is very fulfilling.
